title: Enhancement of the characteristics and HER activity of molybdenum carbide nanosheets for hydrogen evolution reaction
content:
Sustainable Energy Fuels, 2024, Advance Article
DOI: 10.1039/D3SE01625K, Paper
Muhammad Faisal Iqbal, Muhammad Idrees, Muhammad Imran, Aamir Razaq, Guanming Zhu, Jing Zhang, Zahir Muhammad, Meng Zhang
Hexagonal Mo2C-1200 nanosheets exhibited good physical characteristics, which promoted the HER activity. The Mo2C-1200 nanosheets revealed an overpotential of 139 mV, Tafel slope of 44 mV dec−1 and TOF of 304.10 ms−1 in 1 M KOH.
